A.3.5.7  Where a lactation room is provided in a workplace, it should:  

(a) be located in a calm and restful environment;  

(b) offer privacy and protect the user  from being seen by co -workers;  

(c) give consideration to comfort and provide sound privacy surrounding the 
lactation room as breast pumps can be noisy.
